Omaha.Clarinda & Page Apartments: The Clarinda and Page Apartments were located at 3027 Farnam Street and 305-11 Turner Boulevard in the Midtown area of Omaha, Nebraska. Built in 1909 and 1914 respectively, they both reflected the Georgian Revival style of architecture. The buildings were designated an Omaha Landmark on April 21, 1981, and were added to the National Register of Historic Places, as well.
